ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, I would recommend it to all students who are interested in physical chemistry.
Just the required auditing of a p-chem seminar series
Yes, go and take a look at what others are doing.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The course has slightly opened my eyes to what other departments are doing. Towardsmy own research I am learning what makes for a good talk.
This course is my dissertation research.
We should bring the merits from other research field into our research field, and the seminar is very helpful for broadening our horizons.
